reviews.text: good traditional taste

If I classify Cha Chang Ting as taste good or taste bad. I'll put this one in the bad category. Been visited several times and all the dishes I tried were not satisfactory. For instance, fried fish with tomatoes, the fish and the tomatoes are like two separate things that put into the same plate before serving while the tomatoes taste like uncooked... 👎
方便，價格公道。
早餐質素一般，但較特別既係有宮保雞丁同埋漢堡扒揀，在元朗區較少這樣的選擇。
價錢公道。陸拾幾蚊。有湯， 送咖啡或茶，一個小菜，一個白飯。好過自己煮，又唔使洗，又唔使煮
